BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 186.0 720 Td (Chapter 1: Shrinking Down) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Meet Nano! He is the smallest explorer in the world - so small he can) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (travel inside a human body! Today, Nano has a very special mission.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td ('I am going to explore what happens inside you!' Nano announced excitedly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (He put on his tiny explorer hat, grabbed his magnifying glass, and jumped) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td (straight into a glass of water that a boy named Alex was about to drink.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td ('Here I go!' Nano shouted as Alex took a big gulp. The adventure begins!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: YOUR DIGESTIVE SYSTEM) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (When you eat or drink, food enters your mouth and begins an incredible journey.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Your body has a long tube called the digestive system - about 30 feet long!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Its job is to break food into tiny pieces your body can use for energy.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (The journey from mouth to exit takes about 24-72 hours. That is 1-3 days!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (Every part of this system has a special job in breaking down your food.) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 390 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 449 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 429 Td (* Your digestive system is about 30 feet long - as long as a school bus!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 411 Td (* You produce about 1 liter of saliva \(spit\) every single day.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 393 Td (* Your body digests food even when you are standing on your head \(gravity not needed\)!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 360 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 344 Td (Chew a plain cracker for 30 seconds without swallowing. Does it start to taste sweet? That is enzymes!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 324 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 308 Td (Why do you think we need to chew food before swallowing it?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
