BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 176.4 720 Td (Chapter 7: The Defense Army) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Suddenly, alarms went off everywhere! 'Intruder alert!' signals flashed.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (A germ had invaded the body! Nano watched the defense army spring into action.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td (White blood cells rushed to the scene like an army of brave soldiers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (Some cells surrounded the germ and swallowed it whole! Others sent out antibodies.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td ('Antibodies are like guided missiles!' Nano observed. 'They lock onto the germ!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td (Within hours, the invader was defeated. The body was safe again!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: YOUR IMMUNE SYSTEM) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (White blood cells are your body's soldiers - they fight off germs and diseases.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Your skin is the first defense - it acts like armor keeping germs out.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Antibodies are special proteins that remember germs so they can fight them faster next time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Vaccines work by teaching your immune system to recognize dangers before they attack.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (A fever is your body turning up the heat to kill germs that cannot survive high temperatures.) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 390 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 449 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 429 Td (* Your body makes different white blood cells, each with a special job.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 411 Td (* Once you beat a disease, your body remembers it and can fight it faster next time!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 393 Td (* Washing hands for 20 seconds removes 99% of germs. Sing 'Happy Birthday' twice!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 360 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 344 Td (Put glitter on your hands and try to wash it off. See how hard it is to remove all germs!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 324 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 308 Td (Why do you only get chickenpox once? How does your body remember?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
